              After an attempt to try the the first quest in the TL2 beta, I've a bad feeling. It's been a while since I played TL1, so I've no idea what's going in this game. I was assaulted with close to a dozen tips - none of which I can remember due to information overload. The controls weren't explained. I received a collar for my dog as a reward, yet I can't equip it and the game doesn't tell me why. I hit a load screen that basically froze the game up for several minute, so I closed the program. Did I mention that none of the enemies attacked?<br /><br />TL2 didn't leave me with a good impression.

              

              
              
            </div>
